1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
